{"tid":2294892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍機再飛越中國領土！ 這回換白宮國安顧問專機訪越「路過」","createTime":"2020-11-21T10:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T13:33:21.000Z","uid":337052,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3501c78458d2289b4979eb961a7dbb219d86311","tid":2294892,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美軍機再飛越中國領土！ 這回換白宮國安顧問專機訪越「路過」</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/21/phpdHzmYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F21%2FphpdHzmYs.jpg&h=acffae6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白宮國家安全顧問歐布萊恩近日造訪越南，其搭乘之美國空軍C-32A專機被軍事觀察相關自媒體再度捕捉到「飛越中國領土」。（翻攝自「Callsign：CANUK78」推特）<br />\n<br />\n2020/11/21 16:12<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">白宮國家安全顧問歐布萊恩（Robert O'Brien）近日造訪越南，其搭乘之美國空軍C-32A專機被軍事觀察相關自媒體再度捕捉到「飛越中國領土」，並與上次美國國務卿龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）從越南離開的路線雷同。</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，歐布萊恩近日造訪越南及菲律賓，除了討論中國日益加劇的海上軍事行動，也將分別和兩國的領導人會面，確認雙邊的良好關係，以及討論區域安全合作；在此之前，美國國務卿龐皮歐也於上月月底訪問越南河內。<br />\n<br />\n常發布各國公務機航跡的「Callsign：CANUK78」推特昨日下午發文指出，編號為98-0002的美國空軍C-32A專機從日本東京出發，途中飛越中國領空，航經杭州市並一路往南至廣州，再飛抵越南河內，此路線和上次龐皮歐從越南離開的路線雷同。<br />\n<br />\n即使美方同樣未做證實，不過中國知名軍事部落客「戰略之頁7」也發文指出，歐布萊恩確實搭乘此班機從日本橫田基地起飛，飛越中國上空前往越南河內訪問，中國網友則表示「不要緊張，提前報備了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/is_keelu/status/1329717436057333764?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fis_keelu%2Fstatus%2F1329717436057333764%3Fs%3D20&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=da7c084d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fis_keelu%2Fstatus%2F1329717436057333764%3Fs%3D20&h=ae251f36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/is_keelu/status/1329717436057333764?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/21/phpV3iLt2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F21%2FphpV3iLt2.jpg&h=9f00be50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nC-32A專機從日本東京出發，途中飛越中國領空，航經杭州市並一路往南至廣州，再飛抵越南河內，此路線和上次龐皮歐從越南離開的路線雷同。（翻攝自「Callsign：CANUK78」推特）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3358422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3358422&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=00c384f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3358422&h=e085fb89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3358422</a>"},{"pid":"0c6786a111011869bf8aaae2d5c3204504f0b62b","tid":2294892,"uid":194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"LM睇大和田"},{"pid":"c7f75240a4267dcb4a2aa655c83c5ad93b3d3ee9","tid":2294892,"uid":92448,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"支那唔射佢落黎爽下?<br />\n又可以畀小粉紅打飛機, 落鳩美帝面<br />\n唔係覺得打唔贏啊?"},{"pid":"d2608e13090ada397a8e2523abbf066ee3525089","tid":2294892,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.sggp.org.vn/w570/Uploaded/2020/ctcqrvrnw/2020_11_21/ngo_xuan_lich1_vgur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.sggp.org.vn%2Fw570%2FUploaded%2F2020%2Fctcqrvrnw%2F2020_11_21%2Fngo_xuan_lich1_vgur.jpg&h=7ec37e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐布萊恩與越南國防部長<br />\n<a href=\"https://sggpnews.org.vn/national/defence-minister-hosts-us-national-security-advisor-89416.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsggpnews.org.vn%2Fnational%2Fdefence-minister-hosts-us-national-security-advisor-89416.html&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=9ce23c16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sggpnews.org.vn/national/defence-minister-hosts-us-national-security-advisor-89416.html</a>"},{"pid":"16fca320a2601f2ae611f172f978444f07fa3384","tid":2294892,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0c6786a111011869bf8aaae2d5c3204504f0b62b","tid":2294892,"uid":194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"LM睇大和田"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8368c693eeffedd8f6113f7e6b58b23d84a63da1","tid":2294892,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa40602686f45a561d389f4d8ef11569bb64d41","tid":2294892,"uid":166308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"咁樣兜都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5901b2039198440282f33ad22e37d86b47e5e428","tid":2294892,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"好失望<br />\n中國軍機幾時飛返去美國威返次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前我去到邊都敢大嗌「我係中國人」<br />\n而家中國比美帝踩到上心口都忍氣吞聲<br />\n下次見到美國人都唔知點抬起頭望佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae509d0faf2d50227502f7afb201b744a77f7c2d","tid":2294892,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"白宮：Hey，栗米刁，你想我飛支那定飛台灣領空?"},{"pid":"e3e7eaa6da7d991a12154b5ccb85015fb11acb03","tid":2294892,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"最叻打飛機<br />\n都唔打佢落黎<br />\n俾個下馬威 尾國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b613e01bf0f94866cfeabc6d402e7f844463637","tid":2294892,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"其實當有戴住重要人物既飛機飛越人哋領空，一定經過對方同意。否則，真係射落黎，咁點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}